products.description: Hosa Technology 20' Pro Stereo Dual REAN 1/4" TS Male to RCA Male Stereo Audio Cable The Hosa 20' Pro Stereo Dual REAN 1/4" TS Male to RCA Male Stereo Audio Cable is a professional audio cable that is ideal for touring and live sound applications where a device with stereo unbalanced 1/4" outputs needs to be connected to a device with stereo RCA phono inputs. The cable has top-quality REAN connectors for excellent durability and superior signal transfer. The conductors are made from 24AWG oxygen-free copper to maintain a clear signal path. The cable also has 90% OFC spiral shielding for terrific flexibility and effective EMI and RFI rejection. The cable is 20' long and has a pair of 1/4" TS male phone connectors at one end and a pair of RCA male phono connectors at the other.
